-4834.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683987035-7743.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>", "<a href="https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683987035-8310.jpeg">630_360_16839...</a>"]</p>
